summary: A savegame of a pretty bosmer in manacles, saved right after creation.
descriptionHtml:
Cirwen is a lovely little bosmer creature I created and will be sharing with you fine folks on the Nexus.

My Cirwen (pronounced KAI-when) is a timid, light stepping archer who prefers to camp out in the wilderness than venture into stonewalled cities.

To install: Extract the .ess file into your Saves folder. This is usually located in C:\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves. From the Skyrim in-game menu, Load. 
To uninstall: Delete it.

In order for her to look like her picture you will need:

Apachii\'s ApachiiSkyHair: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
Xenius Character Enhancement: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2356
Chanon\'s Younger Females: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3227
NecKros\' Beauty faces for females: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1329
Aluminiumfoil\'s Eyebrows Match Hair: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=627

I also use Dimonized UNP body Skinny version http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709 and Fitness body http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16731 but you can use your body shape and texture of choice.
